\verb{out_dir/gvr_summary/}; set either to \code{FALSE} to skip it. The cohort oncoplot lives
in \code{\link[=gvr_oncoplot]{gvr_oncoplot()}}.

Data conventions:
\itemize{
\item "Missing" means \code{NA} OR empty string \code{""}.
\item Unknown/blank gene symbols are \code{Hugo_Symbol} in \code{c(".", "", "Unknown")};
these are excluded from the distinct-gene tally and from \code{top_genes}, but their
variants are still counted in the totals (and reported as "variants with no
